What you need to know:

The plan will see the devolved unit construct two new facilities as well as rehabilitate at least five.The county government has identified markets including Dandora 1 Market, Ruai, City Park, Shauri Moyo, Karen, Makina and Kariokor Market for the project.Reconstruction of a burnt block at Karen market, awarded Sh10 million in the financial year ended June 30, 2020, has stalled with works only 30 percent done.City Hall is also looking into the setting up of incubation centres to support youth in business startups and entrepreneurship at a similar cost.